OL,3,CGreen Party launches Welsh manifesto
OL,4,Cwith promise to raise taxes on the
OL,5,Crichest
OL,7,FThe Green Party has launched its Welsh
OL,8,Fmanifesto, promising to raise taxes on
OL,9,Fthe richest to fund public services.
OL,11,FThe party will stand in each of the 32
OL,12,FWelsh constituencies for the first
OL,13,Ftime, with the number of Welsh MPs
OL,14,Fdecreasing from 40 at the General
OL,15,FElection following a boundary change.
OL,17,FThe party says they would increase
OL,18,Fpublic service spending in Wales by
OL,19,Fintroducing a wealth tax of 1% a year
OL,20,Fon assets of more than #10m, rising to
OL,21,F2% on assets worth more than #1bn.
